			<ns0:name>euge...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/101600367715055138223/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">If SDL_naclvideo driver is in use, SDL_Quit will cause it to release the PPAPI 2d graphics context. As SDL_Quit is typically called off the main (browser) thread, this ends with an assertion failure in PPAPI code.

SDL_Quit should be made safe to call from any thread.</ns0:content><ns0:updated>2011-10-02T04:13:43.000Z</ns0:updated><ns0:published>2011-10-02T04:13:43.000Z</ns0:published><ns2:status>Accepted</ns2:status><ns2:owner>
